PrecisORDER AMENDING SCHEDULE 1 TO THE CANADIAN ENVIRONMENTAL PROTECTION ACT, 1999 (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) which, for purposes of clarity, adds the salt compound of benzidine to its listing in Schedule 1 to the Act, and makes the terminology used in the listing for "Mirex" consistent with that found in Schedule 3.
